These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, videographer, photographer, librarian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, cottage, palace
City: hamburg, marseilles, hannover, london
1. the ranch-style house is the fan of techno##1
2. the cottage house is between the photographer and the librarian##2
3. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is the photographer##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
9. the videographer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | videographer | librarian   | bartender  | photographer  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| House   | palace | ranch-style | cottage | cape-cod |
| City     | london  | hamburg       | marseilles    | hannover     |

