.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, pink, red, light-blue
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, coffee, fanta
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cabbage, cucumber, carrot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person drinking fanta is between the person eating cucumber and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person drinking fanta and the person eating carrot##2
7. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes red##1
9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | light-blue | pink    | red  | mauve    |
| Beverage   | juice      | sprite  | fanta  | coffee |
| Food           | carrot      | cucumber       | cabbage      | cranberry       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

