.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, australian, british, french
City: hamburg, prague, nizza, edinburgh
House: townhouse, tower, palace, craftsman
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the palace house is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the british is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the tower house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the french is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the thai is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
9. the person traveling to nizza is between the british and the tower house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | australian | british     | thai   | french     |
| City       | prague   | hamburg   | nizza | edinburgh |
| House         | townhouse   | palace | craftsman       | tower    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

