.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, mirinda, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, russian, spanish
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, azure, blood-red, white
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 2. the spanish is the person drinking water##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the spanish is the person who likes azure##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the egyptian is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the british is on the right of the spanish##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes emerald and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | water  | milk | sprite     | mirinda |
| Nationality   | spanish | british  | russian | egyptian       |
| Color           | azure       | white    | blood-red      | emerald           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

