 3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the polish is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the polish##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is the argentine##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the owner of the horse and the indonesian##2
10. the nigerian is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| City           | hamburg | paris | new-york    | hannover     |
| Nationality   | indonesian      | nigerian       | polish    | argentine       |
| Pet         | goldfish     | pony       | horse | snake |

