4 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, goldfish, bird
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, blend, bluemaster, chaman
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the train##1
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the bluemaster-smoker is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | february | january | march  | april  |
| Pet   | cat       | goldfish   | turtle | bird    |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | bluemaster   | chaman | blend |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

