3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the modern house is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the cottage house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
8. the art-deco house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| House      | modern  | cottage   | art-deco    | ranch-style  |
| Birthday   | july    | september   | august | october |
