There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, red, white
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, snowmobile, bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the owner of the goat is the person who likes red##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who likes red is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes white and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | turtle        | rabbit    | pony | goat   |
| Color           | white | grey | turquise   | red |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | quad-bike       | bike      | tram     |
| Sport         | parkour       | volleyball | cycling    | handball  |

