The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, mystery, animation
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Sport   | sailing    | rowing    | surfing      | badminton |
| Birthday       | march        | july       | december       | october     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Movie-Genre        | fantasy       | animation     | mystery         | family           |

